        "id": "4",
        "slug": "sustainable-luxury-future-of-living",
        "title": "Sustainable Luxury: The Future of Living",
        "excerpt": "True luxury is conscious. Exploring how high-end design is leading the way in sustainability without compromising aesthetics.",
        "content": "\n            <p>Sustainability is no longer a choice; it is a necessity. But it doesn't mean sacrificing beauty. In fact, the most sustainable choices are often the most beautiful—timeless, durable, and natural.</p>\n        ",
